nodes.text: Jaiteh Yasin was a Twi'lek ambassador who visited the Cularin system. He was once interviewed by Melanda Forswoth for Eye on Cularin with regard to knowledge on the Caarites and their homeworld of Caarimon.
Yasin appeared at the Peaces interactive adventure as part of the Living Force campaign. He was played by Sean Orwin, pictured here with Sarah Bruner.
